title: Swift and Shift Couriers S01E04 PDTV XviD
description:
Swift and Shift hire two new efficiency managers, Damien and Karen, who change the computer and logistics system. Unfortunately the system crashes and shuts down the depot. The only courier working is Mario who has to deliver a realistic looking sex doll to a farmer in a small town called Gallops Crossing.
